https://promedmail.org/wp-content/uploads/usa-pdf/AUG15USDATASET_1597588305.pdf accessed at 22:04 EDT (GMT-4) and https://promedmail.org/wp-content/uploads/usa-pdf/AUG15US7_1597588353.pdf

